    <h1>Local SEO Predictions 2027: What's Coming Next</h1>
    <p class="description">Eight local SEO predictions for 2027 based on AI Overview data, GBP changes, and the shift to visual and voice search. Built from 3,500+ businesses.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
